chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to start?
si
great! i see us at the starting point with a twig leading to a small island on our left
how should i proceed?
continue straight
okie dokie, we've reached the island with the tiger now
where are we headed next?
continue straight
alrighty, now we're on a bigger island with a parrot on a tree
what's next?
make a c shape on that island
got it, we made a "c" around the island and arrived at the elephant
ok continue to the right
gotcha, we've arrived at the giraffe to the west of the elephant
what's our next move?
go straight to the left
okie dokie, we're back with our elephant friend again! what's our next move?
go straight
alrighty, we're now by a snake south-east of that giraffe
what's next boss?
go up and to the left
gotcha, we're back at the elephant again! where to next?
go south east
ok, we're back at the snake now
where to next?
go up and to the left
got it, we're back with the elephant again! where should we head next?
go south west
alrighty, we're back by the snake again! what's next?
go up and to the left
gotcha, it's deja vu - we're back with the elephant again! what's the next step?
go up slightly and straight
alrighty, we've found our giraffe friend again! where to now?
go west
got it, we're back at the elephant again! next move?
go south west
okie dokie, now we're at the snake again! where to from here?
go up to the right
gotcha, we're now two steps east of the snake and hey, there's the treasure! we made it! *finished*
hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
si
¡genial! vamos a comenzar junto al perro blanco donde te encuentras ahora
quiero que te desplaces algunos pasos hacia la izquierda, por debajo de un banco de madera, y cruces un sendero en camino hacia un puesto de flores. ¿lo ves?
si
¡perfecto! ahora, en lugar de seguir hacia el puesto de flores, haz un giro en u a la izquierda, cruza de nuevo el sendero, y encamínate de vuelta hacia el perro blanco
cual perro blanco? hay dos
oh, discúlpame por la confusión
regresa al primer perro blanco, el que está más cerca del banco de madera. ¡vas muy bien!
ok estoy con el perro
¡buen trabajo! ahora, quiero que cruces un sendero que está al sur, justo sobre el banco del perro blanco y sigue bajando
te encontrarás con otro perro blanco que está junto a un mantel de picnic a cuadros rojos y blancos
ok
ahora, camina sobre el mantel, cerca a un tazón de frutas
continúa hacia la izquierda después de ello
ok
¡fenomenal! ahora hay otra ramita de madera que cruza un río, ve por ahí, cruzando el río hacia el norte
ok
genial, una vez hayas cruzado el río, verás un arbusto verde justo en frente
quiero que lo circules por la derecha hasta alcanzar el puesto de flores. pero cuidado, no lo toques
ok
una vez llegues al puesto, gira a la izquierda, pásalo por debajo y sigue hacia el oeste
hey, estas listo?
si
cool! i'm at the tent on the north part of the map
where do i head next?
go down and pass the dog
got it! i'm now past the dog by the fire
here next?
go on the path near the blue car
awesome, i see the blue car now
so what's next?
make a turn near the blue car and continue to the telescope
alright, i'm at the telescope now! it's pretty cool
where now?
go around the telescope walking in front of a green bush. get back on the path and walk to the cabin
done with the bush, the cabin is in my sights
ok walk onto the big rocks and go to the cabin
perfect! i've arrived at the wooden house surrounded by rocks *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to start?
yes
awesome! see the three palm trees? go under the first one, and head southwest. then take a sharp right, and move past the second tree
before you reach the third one, turn left. now go straight to the south. got it?
yes
awesome sauce! next, see that brown puppy over there? steer left of it
then curve a little to the left and right back to the south. keep trekking!
ok
perfect! now, you're gonna see a big rock on your left and a small one on your right
go right in between 'em, all the way to the water's edge. you're doing great!
got it
sweet! go into the water now, until you spot a large red crab
then go right along the big rock and continue to the west in the water. you with me?
yes
rad! keep going until you're alongside a medium rock
when you see a shark, that's your cue to turn sharp right. trust me on this one!
ok
awesome! now leave the water and go back to the terra firma
move between the medium rock and that funky blue-yellow-white ball. keep going north!
ok
great! now, gently go left towards northwest
look for a rad red tent and a speaker
ok
cool! now, trek between the red tent on your left and the speaker on your right
keep it cool!
ok
nice! now, take a leisurely arc around that red tent
ok
right on! now, head back south towards the water
but wait! don't hit the surf!
ok
great! just as you're about to hit the water's edge, turn right and walk underneath the red kayak
ok
cool! turn a sharp right again, then head north along the kayak until you reach a small green bush
you're almost there!
ok
whoop! you've made it! right where you're supposed to be! killed it, buddy!
yay
you smashed it! excellent job navigating
gracias
de nada, amigo! that was fun, wasn't it?
yes
awesome! if you need another adventure, just holler
happy exploring!
